Answers to the most common questions about GOADS aged Facebook profiles.

### What are aged Facebook profiles?

Aged Facebook profiles are real accounts with a long history, carefully nurtured over time using our proprietary formula. They are much more trusted by Meta than newly created accounts.

### How old are GOADS aged profiles?

Our profiles have ages ranging from 2 to 15 years, depending on the specific product line.

### How does GOADS create aged profiles?

All GOADS profiles are clean farmed and nurtured over a long period. We do not buy, scan, hack, or use stolen accounts from real users. This ensures super high quality and maximum stability.

### What is a USA Profile?

USA Profiles are created and warmed using USA IPs. We apply multiple advanced nurturing techniques across various IPs and devices, then carefully select only the strongest, healthiest profiles to deliver to customers.

### What is an Asia Profile?

Asia Profiles are created and warmed using Asian IPs. They undergo the same rigorous nurturing process with multiple tricks, tested across many devices, and only the highest-quality ones are selected.

### What is the difference between USA and Asia Profiles?

USA Profiles are nurtured and warmed from US IPs, making them stronger and more suitable for the US and European markets. Asia Profiles are optimized for Asian markets. Choosing the right geo helps improve account stability and ad performance in your target region.

### Are GOADS profiles clean with no phone or WhatsApp issues?

Yes. Our profiles are completely clean, they have no phone number or WhatsApp code issues, allowing them to receive Business Managers, Pages, and other assets smoothly without bugs or errors.

### What do I receive when purchasing a profile?

When you buy a GOADS aged profile, you will receive full information including:

1. UID
2. Password
3. 2FA (Two-Factor Authentication)
4. Email + Email Password
5. Cookies
6. And other necessary login details

### Are GOADS profiles phone-verified or email-verified?

Most of our aged profiles are fully verified (email + additional security layers) for maximum stability.

### What is the warranty on aged profiles?

All aged profiles come with a 14-day warranty with unlimited fast & free replacements if disabled under normal usage conditions.

### Can I run ads directly from aged profiles?

Yes, you can. However, we strongly recommend using them inside a Business Manager for better performance, security, and higher spending limits.

### Are the profiles ready to use immediately after delivery?

Yes. You will receive full login credentials and detailed setup instructions. They are pre-aged and ready for configuration.

### Why are GOADS aged profiles better than others?

Because they are clean, long-aged, and carefully nurtured according to GOADS' strict formula, resulting in super high quality, strong stability, and significantly lower disable rates.

### How can I maximize the lifespan of my aged profiles?

Follow our [Security Tips](/docs/questions-bank/security-tips): use consistent proxies, warm up accounts gradually, and maintain natural usage patterns.

### Are your profiles safe to use for big spending campaigns?

Yes. When used with proper setup and proxies, our high-quality aged profiles perform excellently even on large budgets.

